Here’s a professional email template you can use to ask for next opportunities or a full-time role after completing your internship:

---

**Subject:** Interest in Future Opportunities Post Internship

Dear \[Manager's Name],

I hope you are doing well.

As my internship is approaching its conclusion on 25th June 2025, I wanted to take a moment to express my sincere gratitude for the opportunity to be part of \[Company Name] over the past 11 months. It has been an incredibly valuable learning experience, and I’ve enjoyed contributing to the team.

I am very interested in exploring any upcoming full-time opportunities within the organization. I believe my experience during the internship, along with my technical skills and commitment, would allow me to continue contributing effectively in a larger capacity.

Please let me know if there are any roles that align with my background or if there's any process I should follow to apply formally.

Looking forward to hearing from you.

Best regards,
\[Your Full Name]
\[Your Phone Number]
\[LinkedIn Profile or Portfolio – optional]

---

Would you like me to customize this further based on your internship role or achievements?
